      <h2>Why Use Face Products?</h2>
      <p>Face products are essential for maintaining healthy, glowing skin. They help cleanse, hydrate, protect, and treat various skin concerns such as acne, dryness, and aging.</p>
      <h2>Types of Face Products</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cleansers</strong> – Remove dirt and excess oil</li>
        <li><strong>Toners</strong> – Refresh and balance the skin</li>
        <li><strong>Moisturizers</strong> – Hydrate and protect the skin barrier</li>
        <li><strong>Serums</strong> – Target specific concerns like dark spots or wrinkles</li>
      </ul>
